Task
Product of array elements
Write a function productOfElements that takes an arr array as an argument and returns the product of the array's elements.
Use a loop in your solution. Array methods are not allowed.
Example:
• the productOfElements ([1, 2, 4]) function must return 8;
• the productOfElements ([2, 15]) function must return 30;
• the productOfElements ([]) function must return 0.


Solution
function productOfElements (arr) {
let element = 1;
   if (arr.length === 0) return 0;
for (let i = 0; i <arr.length; i ++) {
element = element * arr [i];
}
return element;
}
